body: Jamaica Salt says that Wikileaks only confirmed what people already knew about the Christopher "Dudus" Coke extradition, which "pretty much makes this whole Jamaican govt enquiry completely redundant (at a cost of JA 40 million), but they carry on regardless and the Jamaican people have to eat it."

title: Jamaica: Wikileaks & "Dudus"
